CodeIDE - AI Engine with text, voice, multi language support, 
native language syntax, gaming themes, touch ui suppport, 
code gear like joystick gadget. 
Languages Supported: C, C++, C#, Objective C, 
Java, Javascript, Python, and more. 
Native Languages: Hindi, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam and more.

Accessories: Text Editor, Touch Screen Editor, Voice Box for editing source code based on voice commands, CodeStick (like Joystick in xbox & playstation for programming).
